OL,3,CStill searching for answers: college
OL,4,Chits out at 'ambiguity' of ALN system
OL,6,FTeachers working additional learning
OL,7,Fneeds students say they are still
OL,8,Fwaiting for answers on what the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment's reform will mean for them
OL,10,Fand their pupils.
OL,12,FThe reform has been described as
OL,13,F'ambiguous' by staff at a further
OL,14,Feducation college near Llandovery.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Government began its move
OL,17,Ffrom the old SEN - or special
OL,18,Feducational needs system - to ALN -
OL,19,Fadditional learning needs - back in
OL,20,F2022, and it is due to finish next
OL,21,Fyear.
