OL,6,FThe reform is described as an
OL,7,Fintegrated, collaborative process of
OL,8,Fassessment, planning and monitoring.
OL,10,FBut James Slater, the CEO of Coleg
OL,11,FElidir, a college for students with
OL,12,Fautism and other ALN needs, says that
OL,13,Fthe process of applying for a place
OL,14,Fthere can be difficult and needs to be
OL,15,Fimproved.
