OL,3,CStill searching for answers: college
OL,4,Chits out at 'ambiguity' of ALN system
OL,6,F"The various ambiguity around ALN
OL,7,Freform are clearly a concern because
OL,8,Fwe want to continue to work really
OL,9,Fpositively between funders to make
OL,10,Fsure that young people are served as
OL,11,Fwell as possible.
OL,13,F"We understand that not everyone is
OL,14,Fgoing to have the opportunity to come
OL,15,Fto Coleg Elidyr, much as we would like
OL,16,Fto offer it to as many people as
OL,17,Fpossible who have additional learning
OL,18,Fneeds.
