OL,3,CStill searching for answers: college
OL,4,Chits out at 'ambiguity' of ALN system
OL,6,F"We need to make sure that the process
OL,7,Ffor getting into this facility is as
OL,8,Feasy as possible for parents and
OL,9,Flearners because it's a very difficult
OL,10,Fprocess in so many ways.
OL,12,F"There's lots of uncertainty and often
OL,13,Fdecisions can be made very late in
OL,14,Fterms of where the placements will be
OL,15,Ffunded.
