OL,6,F"Our ambition is to widen our offer so
OL,7,Fwe can take these services outside our
OL,8,Fmain site because we understand that
OL,9,Fas more people are being recognised as
OL,10,Fhaving additional learning needs, the
OL,11,Fneed for this sort of service will
OL,12,Fgrow."
OL,14,FPlaces at Coleg Elidr are currently
OL,15,Ffunded by the Welsh Government but
OL,16,Fsoon that will change to the local
OL,17,Fauthority.
