OL,3,CStill searching for answers: college
OL,4,Chits out at 'ambiguity' of ALN system
OL,6,FThis latest criticism of the system
OL,7,Fcomes after a year of intense focus on
OL,8,FALN provision, with many parents
OL,9,Ftelling ITV Cymru Wales they face a
OL,10,Fdaily battle to get the support their
OL,11,Fchildren require.
OL,13,FIn July, a Senedd committee report
OL,14,Fexposed major shortcomings,
OL,15,Fspecifically revealing that children
OL,16,Fand young people with ALN are being
OL,17,F'let down by decision-makers at the
OL,18,Fmost crucial time in their lives.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
