OL,4,Chits out at 'ambiguity' of ALN system
OL,6,FITV Wales put staff and families'
OL,7,Fconcerns to the Cabinet Secretary for
OL,8,FEducation.
OL,10,FLynne Neagle said the Government is
OL,11,Fworking as hard as they can to
OL,12,Fcomplete the reform.
OL,14,F"I don't want families to be
OL,15,Fstruggling. We are working as hard as
OL,16,Fwe can. We've invested tens of
OL,17,Fmillions of pounds as well. We're
OL,18,Fmeeting monthly with individual local
OL,19,Fauthorities.
